node.text: This was in 2017, in Taxco, Mexico. It was probably my best moment on a bike. I won both runs that day by nearly 2 seconds. Everything clicked and I am proud on how I rode. I was confident and rode hard. I can't wait to go back! @altiusevents @jensonusa @cube.bikes @ethirteencomponents @dvosuspension @topeak @flyracingusa @camelbak @rotorbike @wd40bike @kmcchain @sarisofficial @steadyrack @mudhugger2. #urbandownhill #taxco #mountainbiking #mtb #cubebikes.  Subscribe to my Youtube channel for more of this! Link in bio.

node.text: Injury Update: last week while cruising on a blue trail in the Whistler Bike Park I made a small mistake, slid into a rock and ended up breaking my scapula. Not my worst injury but the most painful one probably. Really a bummer as I was feeling really good on the bike and had plenty of projects for the start of the fall. I'll be missing a couple trips in BC, the Proving Ground event and some more local plans I had. Good news is that I already feel better and should not be off the bike too long. Also I had been filming a lot before the crash so you should still have plenty of content to enjoy until I'm riding again including a big project coming September 9th. Thanks for all your support, my sponsors, the bike patrols and the hospital staff! I hope to never see you again in these kind of circumstances... @propain_bicycles @jensonusa @ethirteencomponents @dvosuspension @gopro @hayesbrakes @topeak @ergonbike @flyracingusa @7meshinc @camelbak @rotorbike @oneupcomponents @julbo_eyewear @wd40bike @kmcchain @timepedals @fizikofficial @sarisofficial @steadyrack @mudhugger2 @goplantx @rokform @trailforks. node.text: This spring I rode a few days with @jacksongoldstone and instantly knew he was going to win some races this year! Congrats on the World Cup wins and now the World Championship title buddy! node.text: Sun Peaks earlier this month was super fun. I managed to catch a few laps with local shredder @wren907. Blown away by his riding at only 10! The video is on my channel. @propain_bicycles @jensonusa @ethirteencomponents @dvosuspension @gopro @hayesbrakes @topeak @ergonbike @flyracingusa @7meshinc @camelbak @rotorbike @oneupcomponents @julbo_eyewear @wd40bike @kmcchain @timepedals @fizikofficial @sarisofficial @steadyrack @mudhugger2 @goplantx @rokform @trailforks.
